2-Login Page : 
 1-login with Email And Password And Active Cookies Or Not
 Validation Is: 
 Email : 

 1-NOT repeat unique serverside
 2-filter for email username@company.domain clientside
 3-trim and remove all slashes and backslashes and qoutations clientside
 4-go to database and check the exist or Not
 Password :

 1-Special Character one or more clientside
 2-The Length More than Or equal 8 clientside
 3-Has At Minimum One number clientside
 4-Has Lowercase letter and Uppercase letter one or more clientside
 5-remove trim and slashes and backslashes and qoutations clientside
 6-add salt value severside
 7-crypt the password after salt value serverside
 cookies :  

 1-ask if active or not by checkbox clientside & serverside
 
